CRUD DEPARTMENT API - Use PostMan

View      GET  http://localhost:8080/api/departments
View Page GET  http://localhost:8080/api/departments/page (Tìm trang key = page, value = 1)
Create product   POST http://localhost:8080/api/departments
          {
              "nameDepartment": "Phong A"
          }
Update product   PUT http://localhost:8080/api/departments/2
          {
              "nameDepartment": "Phong B"
          }
Delete product   DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/departments/2
Search name      GET    http://localhost:8080/api/departments/search-name?nameDepartment=C
                        (Tìm theo giá trị key = nameDepartment, value = C)

CRUD Employee API - Use PostMan

View      GET  http://localhost:8080/api/employees
Create product   POST http://localhost:8080/api/employees
           {
              "idEmployee": "CG125",
              "name": "Pham Van A",
              "age": 20,
              "salary": 50000.0,
              "idDepartment": 6
           }
Update product   PUT http://localhost:8080/api/employees/update?idEmployee=CG125
          {
             "name": "Le Pham Minh Hieu A",
             "age": 20,
             "salary": 50000.0,
             "idDepartment": 6
          }
Delete product   DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/employees/delete?idEmployee=CG125
                        (Tìm theo giá trị key = idEmployee, value = CG125)




